{"title": "Visions", "description": "Deeper questions of life and death, and of God\u2019s relationship to man, are explored in this collection of \u201cdreams\u201d by a noted English novelist and literary critic. A man takes an uncertain step into the next world as his life ends \u2013 Defendants at the Last Judgment hurl their own accusations at the Judge \u2013 An angel arrives on Christmas Eve to guide one soul through a night of despair and doubt \u2013 Flowers in a garden contemplate their own mortality \u2013 What would it mean if the world renounced Christ, or God took Christ away from the world? \u2013 And in a world of the future, pleasure and luxury are pursued \u2026 and children are nowhere to be found. (Introduction by D. Leeson)", "duration": 16118, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "1263", "name": "Coulson Kernahan"}], "coverArt": "https://www.archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCovers3/visions_1009.jpg", "copyright_year": "1905", "genres": ["Fantastic Fiction", "*Non-fiction", "Religion"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "David Leeson"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "David Leeson"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Diana Majlinger"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "TriciaG"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "The Child-Face", "readers": [2827], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/visions_1009_librivox/visions_01_kernahan_64kb.mp3", "duration": 938}, {"section": 2, "title": "The Dream of the Dead Folk", "readers": [2827], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/visions_1009_librivox/visions_02_kernahan_64kb.mp3", "duration": 636}, {"section": 3, "title": "God and the Ant", "readers": [2827], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/visions_1009_librivox/visions_03_kernahan_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1497}, {"section": 4, "title": "The Heavenly Grafting", "readers": [2827], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/visions_1009_librivox/visions_04_kernahan_64kb.mp3", "duration": 142}, {"section": 5, "title": "